data.title: Indian food in a Place called Kennedy's Fried Chicken?
data.text: The food was good but the place needs an overhaul. Very stark and empty. I almost turned around and left but it was recommended by some Indian friends.

data.title: I always enjoy Kennedy's
data.text:
Kennedy's is the perfect quick fill up stop. Cheap, simple chicken meals whether its nuggets, strips, sandwiches, wings, thighs etc you can get it here til almost 4 in the morning most nights, for next to nothing. KFC/Mcdonalds grade eats, so if you're looking for something healthy dont come here. Its nothing fancy but for a group of kids skating the skatepark down the road, leaving a concert at tuxedo junction, or a handful of guys leaving the bar, Kennedy's is that perfect greasy sustinence that keeps the night rolling. 

NOTE: located close to a shady area. Late night trips here can be sketchy. Lots of drunk people, homeless people asking to use your phone or to bum some money, and you can imagine the rest. If youre a small white kid like me i would be careful coming here alone past midnight. I dont let it stop me cus i like Kennedy's!

data.title: Good chicken they can work on costumer service
data.text: Went in to order out chicken guy behind counter didn't want to give me what I wanted I was paying the chicken taste so good but the place had a broken front window and was dirty
